inbodydescription.para: This algorithm mimics the Matlab interp1q method. An explaination of this algorithm: We have points we are interpolating from (x) and points that we are interpolating to (xi). We sort the interpolating from points, concatenate them with the interpolating to points and sort the result. We then construct index r, the interpolation index in x for each point in xi.
